&lt;b&gt;Bitter Lake Neighborhood // Seattle, Washington&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
You should have opened your eyes...&lt;br /&gt;
Then you would have seen...&lt;br /&gt;
The hard &amp;amp; cold face of reality...&lt;br /&gt;
The blatant pain you've caused for all...&lt;br /&gt;
The beauty that cannot be replaced...&lt;br /&gt;
But you failed to follow...&lt;br /&gt;
You with your greed....&lt;br /&gt;
The money in your pocket...&lt;br /&gt;
The Dead Earth around us...&lt;br /&gt;
Now you all fall down on your knees... &lt;br /&gt;
This is the day the Earth caught fire.&lt;br /&gt;
