&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="http://www.flickr.com/photos/mikegreear/4737513469/" title="Video of Oil on Pensacola beach"&gt;&lt;img src="http://farm5.static.flickr.com/4134/4737513469_38b36d0213_m.jpg" width="240" height="135" alt="Video of Oil on Pensacola beach" /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This video was taken days after the oil initially began to wash up, and a lot of the oil had been covered up by the tide when I filmed it.  As such, this video isn't a complete representation of the amount of oil that the beach has gotten, but it is still pretty disheartening nonetheless.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="http://www.flickr.com/people/jessiewhittle/"&gt;Jessica Whittle Photography&lt;/a&gt; posted a photo:&lt;/p&gt;

