&lt;p&gt;Getting closer to sunset on Pensacola Beach.   The parking lot at Casino Beach appears to be a staging area for the oil cleanup crews.  We saw multiple busloads come in and go out in the short time we were there.  Heavy equipment was staged at the bottom of the iconic beach ball water tower.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="http://www.flickr.com/people/jessiewhittle/"&gt;Jessica Whittle Photography&lt;/a&gt; posted a photo:&lt;/p&gt;

