&lt;p&gt;The oil in the gulf didn't stop some from enjoying the waters.  The shores at Casino Beach were mostly clear of oil.  The massive amounts that made landfall earlier this week are gone.  There were still small drops of oil on the shore, though, and some could be seen in the surf.&lt;/p&gt;

