&lt;p&gt;The last parking lot before entering the Fort Pickens area of Pensacola Beach.  I couldn't believe how many people were walking around barefoot!  Sorry the focus is a little off here, but I was trying to be discreet...  I was surprised to see when I was processing the image that she has a blob of oil stuck to the bottom of her foot.  EEW!&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
I have a pair of flip flops that Bailey chewed on some (just a little, but enough I can't really wear them out anymore) that I'm keeping in the car for my oil picture expeditions.  ;)  I won't be too disappointed if they get ruined.  So far only one little blob has marred them but I was able to use the oil clean up station to get it off of them.&lt;/p&gt;

