&lt;p&gt;USGS crews collected samples of the seabed in the nearshore zone of Louisiana and other Gulf Coast states to capture a pre-oil sample of organisms living in the benthic environment.&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
